flowRoot.flowPara: ・Did you know that Fencing is one of the safest sports?
Thanks to the dense metal mesh on the front, and the bib protecting the neck, you can be hit in the face without worries!
In Épée and Sabre, the head is a valid target.

flowPara.flowSpan: Because in Sabre and Épée, your head is a target!
